00:24:34.700 --> 00:24:39.290
A restaurant in Williamsburg
called Traif, which is great.

00:24:39.290 --> 00:24:42.750
One of my good friends runs it.

00:24:42.750 --> 00:24:44.150
Where else?

00:24:44.150 --> 00:24:48.175
Momofuku Ssam Bar
is still amazing.

00:24:51.470 --> 00:24:54.080
L&amp;B Pizza in Brooklyn.

00:24:54.080 --> 00:24:56.800
Really good tomato pie.

00:24:56.800 --> 00:24:57.395
I don't know.

