of coffee from the kiosk

00:25:12.270 --> 00:25:14.207
next door.

00:25:14.207 --> 00:25:15.915
SPEAKER: You're just
missing the hot dog.

00:25:15.915 --> 00:25:18.248
MICHAEL SOLOMONOV: [SCOFFS]
There's something in Philly.

